title: After Effects Tutorials w/ Mikey
description:
Hey, this is Mikey.  I do after effects tutorials.  Right now I am covering adobe after effects CC, but some of my older after effects tutorials were, of course, done with older versions of after effects.  I do a lot of work with green screens, logo animations and more practical stuff,  that you can actually use in your video projects, and not just people exploding and tutorials about muzzle flashes.  

Also, be sure to check out my beginning after effects tutorials.  I have them in a playlist right on the home page of my channel.  
Thanks, and be sure to subscribe and check out other after effects tutorials that I have.

For Sponsorships or Endorsements: please contact my at support@cinemaspice.net

title: Kurzgesagt – In a Nutshell
description:
Animation videos explaining things with optimistic nihilism since 12,013.

We’re a team of illustrators, animators, number crunchers and one dog who aim to spark curiosity about science and the world we live in. To us nothing is boring if you tell a good story.

For updates on our videos and other news from the kurzgesagt universe follow us on Twitter, Facebook, Instagram and LinkedIn.
